Resetting DOSE Indication

  • Make sure the unit is in RATE mode.
  • Press and hold the DOSE button until the display shows the blinking segments (which form a rectangle with vertical and horizontal dashes).
  • Release the DOSE button.
  • Press and hold the DOSE button and CLR/TEST button simultaneously for about 5 seconds.
  • The DOSE indication is reset to "000."
  • Release the DOSE button and CLR/TEST buttons.
  • The Dose indication has now been reset.
